column4: Shows understanding that the Chinese team is trying to help (e.g. “I know you are trying to help” or “I appreciate the effort”)
column6: expresses that you want them to put the supplies back in the aid station (i.e. doesn't give in by allowing them to continue to distribute the supplies)
column8: expresses that you want them to work security (i.e. doesn’t give in by allowing them to work the aid station)
